  comicOfTheDay: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 65c3dc16edb40c248aadcf496d916d7d, type: 3}
  comic: {fileID: 1957828166}
  savedHeader: {fileID: 0}
  audioSource: {fileID: 0}
  newsList:
  - header: Break in at the goverment weapon storage
    readHeader: <link="a"><u>Break in at the goverment weapon storage</u></link>
    text: Goverment weapon storage has been a target of a break in. Just few days
      ago suspicious activity was spotted nearby. The army says some automatic rifles
      and explosives were taken, they wont comment on how this was allowed to happe.
    writer: Ash Slate
    ID: 1
  - header: New kids toy is a hit!
    readHeader: New kids toy is a hit!
    text: The new kids toy called "Jumping fat green noisy elephant" hit the market
      last week and has been soldout all around the city. Every child seems to want
      their own.
    writer: Jenny Moonrounder
    ID: 1
  - header: The Future Party Responds
    readHeader: The Future Party Responds
    text: The future party claims their leader, Ms Grau, was set up and as they arm
      for a re-trial do determine her and her party's fate.
    writer: Silver Scrape
    ID: 1
  - header: compMachine95 scandal
    readHeader: compMachine95 scandal
    text: compMachine95 turns out to be a faulty product, the machine wont start
      due to faulty factory machines. DO NOT BUY ONE!
    writer: Gainsboro - alias
    ID: 1
  - header: DJ blueberry shot found dead
    readHeader: <link="e"><u>DJ blueberry shot found dead</u></link>
    text: DJ blueberry shot has been found shot in the crimston river. He was seen
      near the docks last night, Crimebourgistan police department doesnt know who
      the assaulter is but will look into it.
    writer: Tundora Lead
    ID: 1
  - header: Corruption rumors
    readHeader: <link="f"><u>Corruption rumors</u></link>
    text: Rumors of Mr Pikimusta having something to do with Ms Grau going away,
      almost smells like corruption in some way
    writer: Gainsboro - alias
    ID: 1
